MatchingActorClass: The Actor class to create movie scene tracks for.
DefaultTracks: List of movie scene track classes to be added automatically.
ExcludeDefaultTracks: List of movie scene track classes not to be added automatically.
DefaultPropertyTracks: List of property names for which movie scene tracks will be created automatically.
ExcludeDefaultPropertyTracks: List of property names for which movie scene tracks will not be created automatically.
